messages.message: Ah ok - my Refiner program is not returning results and quits with an unexpected error, must be something else

@Aaron Vontell - I ran into something similar few weeks ago, that the refiner program not returning. My problem was that the job status API stuck at pending and never return. You can check the network tab in the console. I still haven’t fully solved this, it seemed to be an nginx problem  - sometimes restart nginx helped.

I ended up logging something from a UDF and see if the returned data printed out successfully in app-task logs….
